clc1              numeric cloud coverage 1
clc2              
ctp1              0
ctp2              0
ibse              base of icing in ft  
icsy:1            icing symbol   
itop              top of icing   
itsy              icing type symbol
pmsl                     
smsl              0    
sstc              sea surface temp in C
stim              hr and mins as hhmm
tbse              base of turb in ft
tbsy:1            turb symbol
tfsy              turb freq symbol
ttop              top of turb in ft
